'''嗜苯胺顆粒'''（azurophil，或Azurophilic granule）是一種[[苯胺染色|苯胺染色]]下產生的構造。在[[勃艮地染色法|勃艮地染色法]]和[[梅洛|梅洛]]染色法下的[[白血球|白血球]]和[[染色質|染色質]]會成現天青色。嗜苯胺顆粒可能會含有[[髓过氧化物酶|髓过氧化物酶]]、{{le|phospholipase A2}}、酸水解酶、{{le|Elastase}}、[[防禦素|防禦素]]、中性[[絲氨酸蛋白酶|絲氨酸蛋白酶]]、{{le|殺菌/通透性增強蛋白質|bactericidal/permeability-increasing protein}}、<ref name="urlPhagocytes-Neutrophils">{{cite web |url=http://www.dent.ucla.edu/pic/members/neutrophils/neutrophils2.html |title=Phagocytes-Neutrophils |format= |work= |accessdate= |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080821132818/http://www.dent.ucla.edu/pic/members/neutrophils/neutrophils2.html |archivedate=2008-08-21 }}</ref> [[溶菌酶|溶菌酶]]、{{le|cathepsin G}}、proteinase 3，和[[蛋白醣|蛋白醣]]。[[嗜中性球|嗜中性球]]的嗜苯胺顆粒內涵有許多抗菌的[[防禦素|防禦素]]，可以和吞噬病原體的[[食胞|食胞]]融合。

嗜苯胺顆粒又被稱為「原發性顆粒」（primary granules）<ref name="GreerWintrobe2008">{{cite book|author1=John P. Greer|author2=Maxwell Myer Wintrobe|title=Wintrobe's clinical hematology|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=68enzUD7BVgC&pg=PA173|accessdate=10 November 2010|date=1 December 2008|publisher=Lippincott Williams & Wilkins|isbn=978-0-7817-6507-7|page=173|archive-date=2017-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170419121008/https://books.google.com/books?id=68enzUD7BVgC&pg=PA173|dead-url=no}}</ref>

